name: Aaron The All Speaker
description:
The vastness of The Else World makes communication a challenge. Aaron has always been a linguistic prodigy, and he seeks the ultimate understanding of all languages as his life's work.

He is the youngest ever professor in The University of Else World, but he still experiences many adventures as his skills are essential in diplomacy with many alien worlds.

2048 x 2048 pixels, done in Procreate.
